[b]Who I'm Going To Miss:[/b] (in no specific order) -OmgItsShane -imsuperman05 -asshole_rule -LoveandPower -Squirt Ltd -marcbob -Carly -Rash -Vexillum -mr extremez [or whatever lol <3] -ExtremeX-Scape [or whatever lol <3] -arham 4
[b]By the way, there's no credits to that dude who made the HyBriD-PvP client.[/b]
This base doesn't have the Korasi's special or enhanced summoning, mine will ;)
[b]Notes:[/b] -I removed the party room, as none of it was my code. -No anti-leech [like always]. -Lots of skills were edited and made better. -Most memory leaks are fixed. -In-game hiscores fixed [somewhat]. -No rollbacks at all [even if you close the source]. -Etc.
